 (features/ qualities/ traits) but also on the (features/ qualities/ traits) of other 
 competing families who also look (for)  ADBP loans. 
 The competitor's (features/ qualities/ traits) are possible (tools or objects used to do work or measure something) in the borrowing equation. The competitors can 
 be at the village level as well as at the district level 
 where their usuals would influence a particular household's demand for credit without influencing 
 its results, such as consumption and investment. 
